vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of a sanitary sewer easement to Isosceles Development L.P., the abutting owner, containing approximately 2,474 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Cesar Chavez Boulevard and Main Street - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee (This item was deferred on February 23, 2022)
